# Screen Capture

An OSX only hack which allows a webpage to trigger and access a partial
screen capture.

Provided the security issues could be worked out, this thing could be 
a great way to get better bug reports, make informal desktop sharing
easier, and well, what else do you think it could be applied to?

Author: Steve Spencer

Source Code: [http://github.com/lloyd/bp-prompting-sample/tree/master](http://github.com/lloyd/bp-prompting-sample/tree/master)
